data.description: Stop the car! BREAKING NEWS: The seller is offering a generous $11k with the preferred lender towards closing costs, one-year home warranty and a craftsmen ride on lawnmower with a full price offer. Closing must occur on or before March 29, 2024. This appealing home, boasting 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, is ready for your prospective buyer. It has a generously-sized master bedroom with separate vanities for both him and her, and a tranquil back deck. includes an inviting private entrance in-law suite with a kitchen, bedroom, and living room area. The property features a fenced, level backyard with a storage building and is conveniently located just minutes away from I-75, shopping and restaurants.
